<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- Key G (1 sharp). Robust 4/4 with stepwise motion in pickup.
- Two strophes (bars 0-9) with slight variation in RH figuration.
- Middle section (bars 10-17): rising RH line, Eb passing chord (bar 14).
- LH: G2-D3-G3-B3 tonic throughout; Em: E2-B2-E3-G3; D: D2-A2-D3-F#3.

VOICE LEADING HIGHLIGHTS:
- RH ascending line bars 3,8 follows melody stepwise G-A-B-C#-D
- Contrary motion bars 16-17: melody D5-B4-A4-A4, bass D2 stationary

TEXTURE ARC:
- Opening: pickup + bars 1-4, moderate density
- Bars 5-9: same with richer inner voices
- Bars 10-12: Eb passing chord (modal color), rest/breath
- Bars 13-17: climax build with fuller LH, RH ascent
- Bar 18: full G tonic close
-->
